The project was made on Java, allowing Chess to be played on the command line.

The following aspects of Chess are implemented:
Illegal Move Detection
Enpassant
Check
Checkmate
Draw
Resign
Pawn Promotion
Castling

The following aspects of Chess are not implemented:
Stalemate

How to play: 

Note: White goes first
1. Enter a piece's location and its destination, in the format "a1 a2"
2. Enter "Draw" after your move to request a draw from the opponent. The opponent is obligated to accept.
3. Enter "Resign" to forfeit the match.
4. In order to promote a pawn to a piece other than a queen, enter "B", "N", or "R" after the pawn move in order to promote to a Bishop, Knight or Rook, respectively.

